      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "edgevib-ts" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "content": "# data-aggregator Internal Metrics\n\nThe aggregator publishes health metrics to MQTT topic:\n`EdgeVib/{site_id}/aggregator/orangepi/status/health` every 30 seconds.\n\n## Check with:\n```\ndocker logs edgevib-aggregator --tail 20\n```\n\nOr subscribe to the health topic via mosquitto_sub:\n```\nmosquitto_sub -h localhost -t \"EdgeVib/+/aggregator/orangepi/status/health\" -C 1\n```\n\n## Metrics reported:\n- msg_received, msg_deduped, parse_errors\n- rows_written, db_errors\n- mqtt_connected, db_connected, uptime_seconds",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "How to Check data-aggregator Health",
      "type": "text"
    }
